com.petpet.c3po.gatherer
Class LocalFileGatherer

java.lang.Object
  com.petpet.c3po.gatherer.LocalFileGatherer
All Implemented Interfaces:
MetaDataGatherer, Runnable
public class LocalFileGatherer
extends Object
implements MetaDataGatherer

A gatherer of a local file system. It is a Runnable class that reads the meta data files into memory and stores them into a processing queue.

Author:
Petar Petrov

run

public void run()
Runs this gatherer and traverses the file system (optionally in a recursive fashion) . Once the files are gathered, all waiting threads on the locks monitor are notified.
